{"title_page": "List of botanical gardens in Norway", "text_new": "'''Botanical gardens in Norway''' have collections consisting entirely of Norway native and [[endemic (ecology)|endemic]] species; most have a collection that include plants from around the world. There are botanical gardens and [[Arboretum|arboreta]] in all states and territories of Norway, most are administered by local governments, some are privately owned.\n* [[Agder Natural History Museum and Botanical Garden]], [[Kristiansand]]\n* [[Arboretet og Botanisk hage]]<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20051105095618/http://www.uib.no/arboretet/]</ref>, [[Milde, Bergen|Milde]], [[Bergen]]\n* [[Botanisk hage]], [[T\u00f8yen]], [[Oslo]]\n* [[Ringve botanical garden]]<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20060213100749/http://www.ringve.com/english/botanical.html]</ref>, [[Trondheim]]\n* [[Rogaland Aboret]]<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20070429160623/http://www.rogalandarboret.no/index.cfm?id=91902]</ref>, [[Sandnes]]\n* [[Stavanger Botanic Garden]]<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20130831110004/http://stavanger.kommune.no/Tilbud-tjenester-og-skjema/Kultur-idrett-og-fritid/Friluftsliv/Stavanger-botaniske-hage/Stavanger-botanic-garden/]</ref>, [[Stavanger]]\n* [[Arctic-Alpine Botanic Garden]], [[Troms\u00f8 (city)|Troms\u00f8]]\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Botanical gardens in Norway|*]]\n[[Category:Lists of botanical gardens by country|Norway]]\n[[Category:Lists of tourist attractions in Norway|Botanical gardens]]\n", "text_old": "'''Botanical gardens in Norway''' have collections consisting entirely of Norway native and [[endemic (ecology)|endemic]] species; most have a collection that include plants from around the world. There are botanical gardens and [[Arboretum|arboreta]] in all states and territories of Norway, most are administered by local governments, some are privately owned.\n* [[Agder Natural History Museum and Botanical Garden]], [[Kristiansand]]\n* [[Arboretet og Botanisk hage]]<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20051105095618/http://www.uib.no/arboretet/]</ref>, [[Milde, Bergen|Milde]], [[Bergen]]\n* [[Botanisk hage]], [[T\u00f8yen]], [[Oslo]]\n* [[Ringve botanical garden]]<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20060213100749/http://www.ringve.com/english/botanical.html]</ref>, [[Trondheim]]\n* [[Rogaland Aboret]]<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20070429160623/http://www.rogalandarboret.no/index.cfm?id=91902]</ref>, [[Sandnes]]\n* [[Stavanger Botanic Garden]]<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20130831110004/http://stavanger.kommune.no/Tilbud-tjenester-og-skjema/Kultur-idrett-og-fritid/Friluftsliv/Stavanger-botaniske-hage/Stavanger-botanic-garden/]</ref>, [[Stavanger]]\n* [[Arctic-Alpine Botanic Garden]], [[Troms\u00f8 (city)|Troms\u00f8]]\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Norway topics}}\n\n[[Category:Botanical gardens in Norway|*]]\n[[Category:Lists of botanical gardens by country|Norway]]\n[[Category:Lists of tourist attractions in Norway|Botanical gardens]]\n", "name_user": "Paul 012", "label": "safe", "comment": "rmv irrelevant navbox", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_botanical_gardens_in_Norway"}
