ormat=2col}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=Australia|award=Gold|type=album|artist=k.d. lang and the Siss Boom Bang|title=Sing It Loud|relyear=2011|certyear=2011|format=2col}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|format=2col}}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{metacritic album|sing-it-loud/kd-lang|Sing It Loud}}\n\n{{K.d. lang}}\n\n[[Category:2011 albums]]\n[[Category:K.d. lang albums]]\n[[Category:Nonesuch Records albums]]\n\n[[it:Sing it Loud]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox album\n| name         = Sing It Loud\n| type         = studio\n| artist       = [[k.d. lang]] and the Siss Boom Bang\n| cover        = SingItLoud.jpg\n| alt          = \n| released     = {{Start date|2011|4|1}}\n| recorded     = \n| venue        = \n| studio       = \n| genre        = [[Folk rock|Folk]], [[jazz]], [[Pop music|pop]], [[rock music|rock]]\n| length       = 56:38 (Deluxe version)\n| label        = [[Nonesuch Records|Nonesuch]]\n| producer     = k.d. lang, [[Joe Pisapia]]\n| prev_title   = [[Recollection (k.d. Lang album)|Recollection]]\n| prev_year    = 2010\n| next_title   = [[case/lang/veirs (album)]]\n| next_year    = 2016\n}}\n{{Album ratings\n|MC = (74/100)<ref name=metacritic>[http://www.metacritic.com/music/sing-it-loud/kd-lang/critic-reviews Critic reviews at Metacritic]</ref>\n|rev1 = [[Allmusic]]\n|rev1score = {{Rating|4|5}}<ref>[http://www.allmusic.com/album/sing-it-loud-mw0002111306 Allmusic review]</ref>\n|rev2 = [[BBC Music]]\n|rev2score = (favorable)<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/music/reviews/h3gw BBC Music review]</ref>\n|rev3 = ''[[The Guardian]]''\n|rev3score = {{Rating|4|5}}<ref>[https://www.theguardian.com/music/2011/apr/17/kd-lang-sing-it-loud-review The Guardian review]</ref>\n|rev4 = ''[[The Independent]]''\n|rev4score = {{Rating|1|5}}<ref>[https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/reviews/album-k-d-lang-and-the-siss-boom-bang-sing-it-loud-nonesuch-2267841.html The Independent review]</ref>\n|rev5 = ''[[Los Angeles Ti