g|Israel}} || Zahav ({{lang-he|\u05d6\u05d4\"\u05d1 \u05d6\u05d9\u05db\u05d5\u05d9\u05d9\u05dd \u05d5\u05d4\u05e2\u05d1\u05e8\u05d5\u05ea \u05d1\u05d6\u05de\u05df \u05d0\u05de\u05ea}}; Zahav Real-time Credits and Transfers)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.boi.org.il/he/PaymentSystem/ZahavSystem/Pages/Default.aspx|title=Central Bank of Israel website|accessdate=2017-10-26|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170919211107/http://www.boi.org.il/he/PaymentSystem/ZahavSystem/Pages/Default.aspx|archivedate=2017-09-19}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Japan}} || BOJ-NET (Bank of Japan Financial Network System)<ref name=RedBook2003>{{cite journal|author=Bank of Japan|title=Payment systems in Japan|url=http://www.boj.or.jp/en/paym/bojnet/index.htm/|publisher=Bank of Japan|year=2003|accessdate=2017-05-03|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170506165528/http://www.boj.or.jp/en/paym/bojnet/index.htm/|archivedate=2017-05-06}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Jordan}} || RTGS-J<ref>http://www.cbj.gov.jo/pages.php?menu_id=128/ {{dead link|date=April 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Kenya}} || Kenya Electronic Payment and Settlement System (KEPSS)<ref>https://www.centralbank.go.ke/national-payments-system/kepss-rtgs</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Korea}} || BOK-WIRE+ (The Bank of Korea Financial Wire Network, \ud55c\uc740\uae08\uc735\ub9dd)\n|-\n| {{flag|Kuwait}} || KASSIP (Kuwait's Automated Settlement System for Inter-Participant Payments)\n|-\n| {{flag|Lebanon}} || BDL-RTGS (Banque Du Liban \u2013 Real Time Gross Settlement)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bdl.gov.lb/pages/index/7/280/Lebanon-National-Payment-System.html|title=Central Bank of Lebanon website|accessdate=2017-05-03|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170427045804/http://www.bdl.gov.lb/pages/index/7/280/Lebanon-National-Payment-System.html|archivedate=2017-04-27}}</ref>\n|-\n| {{flag|Macedonia}} || MIPS (Macedonian Interbank Payment System)<ref>{{cite web|